        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Male genitalia and female terminalia of Orthocyrtus spp. A-F Metapocyrtus (Orthocyrtus) davaoensis sp. nov. A penis in lateral view B idem. in dorsal view C sternite IX in dorsal view D sternite VIII in ventral view E spermatheca F ovipositor in dorsal view G-L Metapocyrtus (Orthocyrtus) hirakui sp. nov. G penis in lateral view H idem. in dorsal view I sternite IX in dorsal view J sternite VIII in ventral view K spermatheca L ovipositor in dorsal view." , "Figure 3. Metapocyrtus (Orthocyrtus) hirakui sp. nov. everted endophallus, lateral view." , "Figure 2. Metapocyrtus (Orthocyrtus) hirakui sp. nov. A male holotype, dorsal view B female, dorsal view C ditto, male, lateral view D ditto, female, lateral view." , "Figure 1. Metapocyrtus (Orthocyrtus) davaoensis sp. nov. A male holotype, dorsal view B female, dorsal view C ditto, male, lateral view D ditto, female, lateral view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529749" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529748" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529747" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529746" .

